title: GCPE #6 - Standard Marketing Campaigns (UTM codes) Results - By Day

dashboard_elements.note_text:
Filter - Date: Input the date range you want to view results for. Results are broken down by individual days. Results are currently available for the last completed 24 months.
Filter - Site URL: Input the site URL or URLs if you want to view results for all of the pages of one or more sites. A reminder to input the different versions or spellings of the site URL to capture all results. For example, www.cleanbc.gov.bc.ca and cleanbc.gov.bc.ca are two versions of the site URL for CleanBC.
Filter - Page URL: Input the page URL or URLs if you want to view results for a specific page or pages. A reminder to input the various potential URL spellings. For example, include and not include the "www"; include and not include the "/" at the end of the URL; etc.
Filter - Marketing Campaign: Input the Marketing Campaign (UTM tracking code) that you want to view results for.
View or Download More Rows/Columns of Data: The current live view limit is 25 rows & 50 columns. To view or download more rows/columns of data, use the "Advanced data options" of the "Download Data" option. Go to the online guide for instructions.
